casebody.data:
King, Respondent, v. Link et al., Appellants. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. December 23, 1891.) Appeal from third district court. Action by Hugh King against George L. Link and others.

Argued before Bookstaver arid Bisohoff, JJ.

F. A. Camp, for appellants. J. A. O’Gorman, for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs.
